            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099102/Van Dale Ne-En (1991)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>標有橫向刻痕的木棍或木棒，用來計算或測量債務或報償。沿刻痕縱向劈開該木棍，債務人和債權人各持有一半，即構成合法債權證明。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
